				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"><span style="font-weight: bold">JT's Final Thought</span>
<br />

<br />
...and as we come to the end of our discussion, I have one Final Thought(tm).  As an Evocation Mage you have no alternative to the Big Bang on FR MOBs, any MR nukes you toss out are not within your specialization so on FR MOBs you are at a complete disadvantage.  Your Conjouration based friend can cast MR nukes, but also on completely MR MOBs he can cast FR nukes within his specialization, i.e. Ancient: Shock of Sun and Shock of Fiery Blades.
<br />

<br />
So take care of yourselves...and each other.<br />_________________<br /><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="left"><tr><td><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=26797"><img src="http://www.jtbates.net/everquest/images/jtshieldtransparent.gif" border="0" /></a></td><td><a href="http://www.fohguild.org">[Fires of Heaven]</a> - <a href="http://forum.magecompendium.com/tower/viewtopic.php?t=3239">[Magician's Tower Library]</a></td></tr></table><br></span><span class="gensmall"><br /><br />Last edited by Jaytee Bushwacker on Fri Mar 28, 2003 9:02 pm; edited 1 time in total</span></td>
