Anyway, small detail JT.  The averages for the foci that are random are: 1-x%.  that means for the bracelet it would be (20-1)/2 + 1 = 10.5% average and for the earring it would be (15-1)/2+1 = 8% average.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=106710" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://www.lehigh.edu/~dsf3/EQ/rhionsligo.jpg" border="0" />
