<br />
And here's a point well worth making... a "combat situation" which requires a non-nuke conjuration spell.  
<br />

<br />
7.5% savings isn't worth that much here, and reality is that given the amount of group switching that usually goes on with coh'ing an entire raidforce into place, I have plenty of time to cannipet to regain mana.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=171313&resize=true" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="font-weight: bold">Eloina Pyromancer</span></a> -- Arch Mage
